name: Nap Time (Jackgalaga)
description:
WASD to move

Space to Jump, Walljump and To Start the Game

Join the miscellaneous cat on its journey to its bed while the house it's living in is getting weirder and weirder, for the cat is dreaming it all

This game was created for the Lost Cartridge Jam 4 in 72 hours
